data.name: seqImportModeBox.ToolTip
data.value: What program should be used to import sequences. Nitro Studio is my importer, Midi2Sseq is the exe included, and Nintendo's tools will use Nintendo's tools if you put them in the same place as Nitro Studio 2. I recommend using Nintendo's tools if possible, but my importer should work pretty well if not as good.
